ers a nice range of topics, with podcast episodes focused on how to write a fiction novel, headline tips, how to not be the \u201cnice guy,\u201d and how to influence the hell out of people. Settle\u2019s irreverent, cheeky, and fun podcast is certainly worth an ear-full.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Average Episode Length:<\/strong> 15 \u2013 20 minutes<\/p>\n<p><strong>Updated:<\/strong> Weekly<\/p>\n<p>Find it on <a href=\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/antipreneur-ben-settle-show\/id812328044\">iTunes<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/www.stitcher.com\/podcast\/ben-settle\/antipreneur-the-ben-settle-show\">Stitcher<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>19. Marketing Growth Podcast<\/h2>\n<p><strong>In the\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/shanebarker.com\/podcast\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Marketing Growth Podcast<\/a>,\u00a0Shane Barker brings to you one of the most informative podcasts out there where he interviews marketing experts and legends twice a week! Each episode is packed with groundbreaking marketing tips and revelations. But that doesn\u2019t mean it\u2019s all work and no play. There\u2019s a fun segment in each episode and your favorite marketers also give you a sneak peek into some crazy moments from their lives. Trust us, you don\u2019t want to miss this one.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Average Episode Length:<\/strong> 15 \u2013 30 minutes<\/p>\n<p><strong>Updated:<\/strong> Every Monday and Wednesday<\/p>\n<p>Find it on <a href=\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/marketing-growth-podcast\/id1472142690\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iTunes<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.stitcher.com\/show\/content-that-converts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Stitcher<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><strong>Not Marketing Per Se<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>These podcasts don\u2019t fit perfectly under the umbrella of marketing podcasts, but I still think you absolutely have to check these ones out.<\/p>\n<h2><strong>The Tim Ferriss Show<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Tim Ferriss, best known for his best-selling book, <em>The 4-Hour Workweek, <\/em><\/strong>explores strategies and tools to help make you a better entrepreneur as well as a happier and healthier individual.\u00a0While not strictly about marketing, the Tim Ferriss podcast deals a lot with topics concerning productivity, efficiency, and mental health \u2013 all topics essential for any great marketer!<\/p>\n<p><strong>Average Episode Length:<\/strong> Varies dramatically \u2013 anywhere from 30 minutes\u00a0 &#8211; 2 hours<\/p>\n<p><strong>Updated:<\/strong> Weekly<\/p>\n<p>Find it on <a href=\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/the-tim-ferriss-show\/id863897795\">iTunes<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/www.stitcher.com\/podcast\/the-tim-ferriss-show\">Stitcher<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><strong>The Art of Charm Podcast<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>The Art of Charm is another podcast that can\u2019t fit uncomfortably under the marketing umbrella, but is still a great podcast worth listening to.\u00a0AJ and Jordan Harbringer provide valuable tips and advice on dating, productivity, networking, building confidence, and the mysterious topic of \u201cbiohacking.\u201d Definitely give their adventurous podcast a listen!<\/p>\n<p>This one is mostly geared towards the men, but women could enjoy it as well.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Average Episode Length:<\/strong> 30 \u2013 60 minutes<\/p>\n<p><strong>Updated:<\/strong> Every few days<\/p>\n<p>Find it on <a href=\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/art-charm-confidence-relationship\/id212382281\">iTunes<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/www.stitcher.com\/podcast\/art-of-charm\/pickup-podcast-9283\">Stitcher<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><strong>Freakanomics<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Freakonmics has been a favorite podcast of mine for a couple years now. Don\u2019t be turned off by the \u201ceconomics\u201d sound (I have to admit, I put off listening for a long time because I assumed it would be dry and dull).<\/p>\n<p>This podcast is packed with absolutely <em>fascinating <\/em>studies and stories, demonstrating how economic theory can be found in everything from dating websites to terrorism.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Average Episode Length:<\/strong> 45 minutes<\/p>\n<p><strong>Updated:<\/strong> Every week<\/p>\n<p>Find it on <a href=\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/freakonomics-radio\/id354668519\">iTunes<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/www.stitcher.com\/podcast\/freakonomics-radio\">Stitcher<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Do you have any favorite podcasts to send our way? Share your top tune-ins in the comments!<\/p>\n<h2>You might also like&#8230;<\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2016\/01\/11\/social-media-marketing-tips\">Our 13 Best Social Media Marketing Tips EVER<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Looking for marketing podcasts to listen to while driving or at the gym? Here are our 18 favorite marketing podcasts to entertain you while you learn.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":206,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-27848","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-marketing-ideas"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>The 19+ Best Marketing Podcasts: Learn With the Pros<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Looking for marketing podcasts to listen to while driving or at the gym? Here are our 18 favorite marketing podcasts to entertain you while you learn.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"noindex, follow\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"The 19+ Best Marketing Podcasts: Learn Wit